komainu
=======

A very simple text search tool.


## Examples

### Simple Search

```ruby
:example:
item1 = OpenStruct.new
item1.text = "hello"
item2 = OpenStruct.new
item2.text = "world"
searchables = [item1, item2]
Komainu.search("world", searchables)

#=> {:suggestion=>nil, :items=>["world"]}
:end:
```
